thread.title: Jeremy

author: Jeremy
title: Jeremy
text: I've been looking for this particular part for over a year - constantly listed on 'back order' at the local dealership. Even though I wasn't familiar with eEuroparts, I took a gamble and ordered the part. It was shipped out within a few days and installed yesterday. Really glad that everything went well - website was easy to use, shipping was fast, and most importantly - the part is new and works as it should! Thanks.
